          <div class="faq-answer">AI writing tools generate drafts that you edit and publish. Automated content creation tools handle the full workflow: writing, optimizing, and publishing without manual steps. Most tools marketed as "automated" are actually AI writing assistants that accelerate drafting but don't replace the pipeline.</div>
